        <h1>Glial Biology,<br/><em>Epigenetics &</em><br/>Neurotoxicology</h1>
        <p>
          I am a postdoctoral researcher with a Ph.D. in Toxicology from <strong style="color:var(--text)">CINVESTAV-IPN</strong>, Mexico City. My work sits at the intersection of glial cell biology, epigenetic regulation, and computational approaches to understanding neurodegeneration.
        </p>
