<!-- ══════════ RESEARCH ══════════ -->
<section id="research">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label">Research</div>
    <h2>Research Areas</h2>
    <p class="research-intro" style="color:var(--muted)">
      My research integrates wet-lab and computational approaches to understand how glial cells regulate excitatory neurotransmission through epigenetic mechanisms — and how these processes break down in neurodegeneration.
    </p>

    <div class="cards-grid">

      <div class="card fade-in">
        <div class="card-thumb thumb-epi" style="font-size:2.6rem; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;">🧬</div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3>Epigenetic Regulation</h3>
          <p>Dynamic DNA methylation control of glutamate transporter genes (SLC1A2, SLC1A3) in glial cells via AMPA receptor signaling cascades.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card fade-in" style="transition-delay:0.1s">
        <div class="card-thumb thumb-glia" style="font-size:2.6rem; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;">🔬</div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3>Glial Cell Biology</h3>
          <p>Functional studies of Bergmann and Müller glia — key support cells for Purkinje and retinal neurons — in glutamate homeostasis.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card fade-in" style="transition-delay:0.15s">
        <div class="card-thumb thumb-neuro" style="font-size:2.6rem; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;">⚗️</div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3>Neurotoxicology</h3>
          <p>Oxidative stress and mitochondrial dysfunction in metal-induced neurotoxicity modeled in <em>Drosophila melanogaster</em>; curcumin as a neuroprotective agent.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card fade-in" style="transition-delay:0.2s">
        <div class="card-thumb thumb-comp" style="font-size:2.6rem; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;">💻</div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3>Bioinformatics</h3>
          <p>ENCODE ChIP-seq mining, CpG island profiling, histone modification mapping, and genome browser analysis with Bioconductor and Python pipelines.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card fade-in" style="transition-delay:0.25s">
        <div class="card-thumb thumb-drug" style="font-size:2.6rem; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;">💊</div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3>Computational Drug Discovery</h3>
          <p>Structure-based drug design, molecular docking (AutoDock/Vina), virtual screening, and AlphaFold structure prediction and refinement.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card fade-in" style="transition-delay:0.3s">
        <div class="card-thumb thumb-circ" style="font-size:2.6rem; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;">🕐</div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3>Circadian Neuroscience</h3>
          <p>Circadian modulation of glutamate uptake activity in retinal Müller cells; collaboration with Prof. Felder-Schmittbuhl (INCI Strasbourg).</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

